OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening for most with a few light
OL,7,Fshowers around. Clear spells along the
OL,8,FMoray Coast will develop more widely
OL,9,Facross most areas overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FDry through the morning and
OL,12,Ffor much of the afternoon with good
OL,13,Fsunny spells. Turning cloudy with some
OL,14,Fshowers spreading east through late
OL,15,Fafternoon and evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
