OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,6,Fmixture of sunshine and showers on
OL,7,FTuesday and Wednesday, the showers
OL,8,Fwintry on the hills. Some rain
OL,9,Fpossible on Thursday. Feeling cool for
OL,10,Fthe time of year.
